</tr>
<tr>
<th>Re:</th>
<td>Incident ███-███</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Attached:</th>
<td>1 file (postincidentaffidavit.pdf)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Dated:</th>
<td>12th March 2015</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th colspan="2">Message</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2">Dear Dr. Fletcher,<br />
<br />
Attached are the Incident Reports from 25/02/2015 regarding SCP-███ testing, including several sections of testimony you provided with regards to the breach that occurred. Site Director Daniels has requested your affirmation of the testimony you provided. Please fill out these forms and submit them by 26/03/2015.<br />
<br />
Kind regards,<br />
S. R. Samuel Morgan</td>
</tr>
</table>
