<td>Site Director Janet Daniels</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Re:</th>
<td>Application of Leave (12/03/15)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Dated:</th>
<td>14th March 2015</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th colspan="2">Message</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2">Dear Dr. Fletcher,<br />
<br />
Your request for leave has officially been approved, effective from 15/03/2015 to 05/04/2015.</td>
</tr>
</table>
<hr />
<table class="wiki-content-table">
<tr>
<th>To:</th>
