<tr>
<th colspan="2">Message</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2">Scott,<br />
<br />
I know you probably won't read this until you come back to your office in a few weeks, but when you do get around to reading this, I want to talk to you. If you don't want to talk to me, that's fine, but I saw you in the hall a couple of days ago. To put it kindly, you really look like you need to talk to somebody. Whether or not that person's me, I don't care, but please.<br />
<br />
Get better soon.<br />
<br />
Adileh</td>
</tr>
