<tr>
<td colspan="2">Sorry to bother you again, Adileh, but this Sam guy keeps picking on me whenever I tell him that &quot;no, Scott's not coming back this week.&quot; Could you get someone upstairs to tell him to bugger off if he keeps asking? Thanks.<br />
<br />
