<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Technical Report (30th of March, 2015)</strong></p>
<hr />
<table class="wiki-content-table">
<tr>
<th>Ticket #:</th>
<td>1182931230</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Severity:</th>
<td>High</td>
